# Everest Trade — Core

- User language: Russian (Cyrillic). Technical artifacts: English.
- UI language switcher labels: **RU | ENG | CHI** (not ZH/ZHE). Chinese content: 中文.
- Positioning: large-scale international B2B trading; **business partner** tone. Not startup, not founders.
- Do **not** emphasize Russia→China as primary narrative.
- Design taste: clean, presentable, premium corporate. No visual clutter, no muddy/darkened palettes, no neon/AI-purple gradients.
- Read `docs/design-taste.md` before UI work. Offer 2–3 font/color bundles for approval.
- Domain `everestcentr.com` connects **last**, after site is ready. Logo TBD — use text wordmark.
- WeChat: button in header/CHI section; QR placeholder until real QR provided.
- When unsure: `AskQuestion` with Russian options + «Другое / скажу голосом».
- After significant decisions: update `docs/*.md` and `docs/agents-log.md`; tell user in Russian.
